# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Rust (backend/)
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
backend/target/
**/*.rs.bk
Cargo.lock

# Note: Cargo.lock for binaries (like this backend) SHOULD be committed.
# Uncomment the line above only if this is a library crate.
# For the backend binary, keep Cargo.lock tracked.
!backend/Cargo.lock

# SQLx prepared queries cache (commit these for offline CI builds)
# backend/.sqlx/

